{
  "texts": [
    "For this purpose, this survey is organised as follows.",
    "We start with Sect. 2 presenting some generalities about entity linking, recognition and disambiguation.",
    "Then, we present in Sect. 3 the most recent previous surveys that we analysed.",
    "Section 4 presents the methodology that we followed to construct this survey and the research questions that we aim to answer.",
    "We divided the surveyed works into two categories: Section 5 focuses on research on the English language, and Sect. 6 presents multilingual research."
  ]
}